Restricciones respecto a distancia umbral para agrupamiento de usuarios
 en downlink y uplink 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "Non-Orthogonal Multiple Access (NOMA) in Cellular Uplink and Downlink: Challenges and Enabling Techniques-1"
literal "false"

\end_inset


\end_layout

